author: @yona5357
text:
TTT stands for MT SVT RealiTy.
MT stands for Membership Training. Basically it's like a recreational retreat for students/clubs/workers where you go somewhere (usually rural) and bond as a group by cooking and drinking and playing games.
TTT is a bit more special than other episodes since they usually spend 2 days filming them being on vacation. But it's still considered as normal gose since it's a series with many seasons (like Don't Lie, Insomnia Zero, Logic Nights, Bad Clue, etc.). Carats always look forward to TTT cuz there's usually no script (what i mean is that they don't have to dress up as concepts and play the games that ekip prepared), just them playing and drinking, spending the night 2gether. 
You can search for previous seasons (if I'm not mistaken, TTT has the most seasons out of all series in Gose). The first season was in 2018, then 2019, 2020, 2021 and this video is the latest.
